text: Hwang Min-kyoung (born ) is a South Korean female volleyball player. She is part of the South Korea women's national volleyball team. == Career == She participated at the 2011 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix, 2017 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix, 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Grand Champions Cup. == Clubs == * Hyundai Construction, 2011 * Hyundai Construction, 2017 == References == == External links == * FIVB Profile Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean women's volleyball players Category:Asian Games medalists in volleyball Category:Volleyball players at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for South Korea
